<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.2">
<l>vaṇṇap pavaḷa maruṅkiṉiṟ cātti</l>
<l rend="indent">malarppātak kiṇkiṇi yārppa</l>
<l>naṇṇit toḻumavar cintai piriyāta</l>
<l rend="indent">nārā yaṇāviṅkē vārā</l>
<l>yeṇṇaṟ kariya pirāṉē tiriyai</l>
<l rend="indent">yeriyāmē kātuk kiṭuvaṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṇukku naṉṟu maḻaku muṭaiya</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṉakak kaṭippu mivaiyā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having adorned beautiful coral on [your] waist,</l>
<l>while the bells on [your] blossom[-like] feet jingle,</l>
<l>O Nārāyaṇā who is not separate from the minds</l>
<l>of those who approach and worship - Come here!</l>
<l>O Lord who is difficult to contemplate!</l>
<l>I will put the thread [through your] ear without [any] pain at all.</l>
<l>These gold earrings are good for the eyes and are beautiful.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
